<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Quinoa Bowl Recipe</h1>
    </header>
    <section>
        <h2>Ingredients</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>1 cup cooked quinoa</li>
            <li>1/2 cup diced vegetables (carrots, bell peppers, etc.)</li>
            <li>2 tbsp hummus</li>
            <li>1/4 cup chickpeas</li>
            <li>1 tsp olive oil</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Instructions</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Cook quinoa as per package instructions.</li>
            <li>In a bowl, combine quinoa, vegetables, and chickpeas.</li>
            <li>Top with hummus and drizzle olive oil.</li>
            <li>Mix well and enjoy!</li>
        </ol>
    </section>
